{"tid":908264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"休班警遭爆樽圍毆　被指「好X寸」","createTime":"2018-11-19T12:46:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-20T03:33:57.000Z","uid":58335,"like":47,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"e51ea2955f08c3c706a69f2d53ef4d9fc7699277","tid":908264,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:46:42.000Z","msg":"笑撚到我<br />\n身為差佬<br />\n個fd比人打<br />\n2條友第一時間走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】休班警去年與友人到元朗酒吧消遣，友人與鄰枱爭執被玻璃樽掟頭流血，休班警不滿被酒吧要求賠償，外出尋兇之際，於街頭再與另一班男子爭執，其間有人自稱「我南邊圍勝和」，休班警更被10人追打，拳打腳踢兼「爆樽」。一名廚師其後被捕，昨在區院認罪，求情指稱是休班警等人爆粗及「好X寸」，才令他衝動犯案。<br />\n記者：蔡少玲<br />\n<br />\n任職私房菜館廚師的被告關竣豪（23歲），承認於去年7月4日在元朗水車館街自稱三合會成員，並於青山公路與安樂路交界的天橋底，對休班警曾一峰身體加以嚴重傷害，下周一判刑。<br />\n案情指，當日與休班警曾一峰同行的為另一休班警譚信耀。兩的朋友在酒吧內遇襲時，因情況混亂，曾和譚走出店外，後來行兇者離開，他們返回酒吧，見友人受傷流血，而酒吧負責人要求他們賠償3,000元。<br />\n官不接納被告是衝動<br />\n他們認為負責全數不合理，遂外出找行兇者。曾於水車館街與被告等人相遇，被告稱「你搵人啊，X你老母，我南邊圍勝和」，被告又指曾等人「好X寸」，其後曾遇襲。事後曾送院驗傷，證實上肢與背部有擦傷，左側頭皮有血腫和擦傷，腰部有瘀傷。<br />\n辯方求情稱，被告當晚因與朋友慶生而到酒吧飲酒，被告在酒吧外碰到休班警及其友人時，因對方以粗言穢語和不友善的語氣質問他，雙方因而發生口角，被告受酒精影響下才自稱三合會成員。<br />\n辯方又指，被告當時不知道對方是警員，犯案只是一時衝動，衝口而出，並非有任何目的；惟法官不接納被告是衝動而為，也不認為被告純為「吹噓一下咁簡單」。辯方則稱被告在襲擊事件上只是赤手空拳，無證據指他當時攜有武器或扮演領導角色。<br />\n案件編號：DCCC1124/16<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170525/20032863\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170525%2F20032863&d=T1O8ISjNybup5kKBp67ouzPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6e51add2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20170525%2F20032863&h=33eada71\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20170525/20032863</a>"},{"pid":"9148ad343fa916c654b72c7566828f4fdabfaca3","tid":908264,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:50:39.000Z","msg":"戇鳩仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36e98e6cfbbb90849f59429713c4b53b08c0f2a","tid":908264,"uid":62011,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"往死裏打"},{"pid":"6e844e5ea4c71db87da6772914c455bb4f540f92","tid":908264,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:53:16.000Z","msg":"冇做錯喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ca7460f42c3847c7f81bb32061047f7f85a4aac","tid":908264,"uid":201604,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:54:42.000Z","msg":"全部都抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe52d4403b2ebec725ccd42f0b69cd3e89355a6","tid":908264,"uid":214534,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死喇<br />\n一邊就村屋廚師<br />\n笑撚死<br />\n以為自己有丁權大撚晒咩<br />\n又咪係做廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"ec15cb8d100ac06386fdb8fef5eee5742bff00f7","tid":908264,"uid":171409,"like":4,"dislike":9,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"1fe52d4403b2ebec725ccd42f0b69cd3e89355a6","tid":908264,"uid":214534,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-19T12:57:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死喇<br />\n一邊就村屋廚師<br />\n笑撚死<br />\n以為自己有丁權大撚晒咩<br />\n又咪係做廚師<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-1